title: Motorcyclist killed in three-vehicle crash
title_page: Motorcyclist killed in three-vehicle crash near Towcester - BBC News
maintext:
A motorcyclist has died in an accident involving his bike and two cars.
It happened on the A5 near Towcester, Northamptonshire, at about 11:30 GMT on Sunday.
Northamptonshire Police said the incident involved a black Yamaha motorbike and a silver Hyundai travelling north towards Towcester and a blue Volvo heading in the opposite direction.
The motorcyclist, who was in his 30s, died at the scene.
